videoSnippet.title: Garry Kasparov vs Goran Martić (My Brother-in-law) - A High Noon in Croatia
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator You already met Goran Martić on my 50k Subs stream, so I thought I'd show you a game he played against the Beast of Baku :)
The game was played during a renaissance fair in Koprivnica, Croatia.

Garry Kasparov vs Goran Martić
Simultaneous Exhibition in Koprivnica, Croatia
27.8.2016.
Ruy Lopez Opening: Cozio Defense (C60)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nge7 4. Nc3 a6 5. Bc4 Ng6 6. d3 Be7 7. h4 d6 8. h5 Nf4 9. Bxf4 exf4 10. Qd2 Ne5 11. Qxf4 Nxc4 12. dxc4 Bf6 13. Nd5 Be7 14. h6 g6 15. O-O-O Be6 16. c5 Bxd5 17. Rxd5 c6 18. Rd3 Qa5 19. cxd6 Bd8 20. d7+ Kf8 21. Kb1 Qc5 22. e5 Qe7 23. Rhd1 Rg8 24. e6 f6 25. Ng5 f5 26. Nf7 a5 27. Nxd8 Rxd8 28. Qc7 g5 29. Qxa5 f4 30. Qf5+
